        descLong: "Heatmaps show a 2D grid of values where each cell's color represents its magnitude. They are ideal for correlation matrices, 2D density plots, and calendar views. Use Canvas for performance (each cell is a fillRect), D3 for interactivity (hover, tooltips). Color scales (sequential, diverging) map values to colors.",
