        id: "bar-line-chart",
        fn: "Bar & Line Charts",
        desc: "The two most common chart types — categorical comparison and trend over time.",
        category: "Charts",
        subtitle: "Bar: compare categories. Line: show trend over continuous axis.",
        signature: "Chart.js | D3 | Recharts | ECharts",
        descLong: "Bar charts compare values across discrete categories. Line charts show trends over a continuous axis (usually time). Key decisions: bar for categorical, line for continuous; start y-axis at 0 for bar charts (not for line); order bars by value (not alphabetically) for readability; limit categories to ~12 for clarity.",
